title: Property maintenance
text: Property maintenance relates to the upkeep of a <a href="home">home</a>, <a href="apartment">apartment</a>, rental <a href="property">property</a> or <a href="building">building</a> and may be a commercial venture through a property maintenance company, an employee of the company which owns a home, apartment or a <a href="self-storage">self-storage</a> pastime for example day-to-day housekeeping or cleaning.
